4 August 2008Government will hold Cluster media briefings on the decisions taken at the recently held July Cabinet Lekgotla from 5 to 8 August 2008. The purpose of the July Cabinet Lekgotla was to conduct a mid-year review of the implementation of government s Programme of Action (PoA) and to adopt a Medium Term Strategic Framework (MTSF). The briefings will take place at the Union Buildings, Room 153 and Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape Town. There will be a video link-up at all briefings.: Briefing schedule: Note: The Social, Economic and IRPS Clusters are still to be confirmed. Enquiries Harold Maloka (Pretoria) Cell: 082 847 9799 Colin Cruywagen (Cape Town) Cell: 082 377 9916 Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)top